skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: oscar's quotes
des: Oscar Wilde Quotes will keep your mind active with many of the perplexing, altruistic quotations that were part of the creative mind that was Oscar Wilde. Simply tell Alexa to ask Oscar Wilde for his favorite quote, and you will hear any one of over 250 quotes that he said throughout his amazing life.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
